class=default-block><div
class=container-fluid><div
class=default-block__content><p>Thank you for choosing <?=$ihost?> ! We are committed to delivering a seamless experience for our customers. This Delivery Policy outlines the terms and conditions related to the delivery of our software services.</p>
    <h3>Delivery Process</h3>
    <p>Upon completing your purchase, you will receive an email confirmation with instructions on how to access your account and activate your subscription. Our online services are typically delivered automatically, and no physical shipment is involved.</p>
    <h3>Delivery Timeframe</h3>
    <p>The delivery of our software services is typically instantaneous or within a few minutes of purchase. However, in rare cases, delays may occur due to technical or processing issues. If you do not receive your access instructions within 24 houres, please contact our customer support team at support@<?=$ihost?> for assistance.</p>
    <h3>Delivery Methods</h3>
    <p>The delivery of our online services primarily relies on online access means. This includes:</p>
    <ol>
        <li>Access Credentials: You will receive login credentials (username and password) via email or through our website’s secure login portal.</li>
    </ol>
    <p>Please note that it is your responsibility to ensure that the email address provided during the purchase process is accurate and accessible. We are not liable for any delivery issues arising from an incorrect or inaccessible email address.</p>
    <h3>Technical Requirements</h3>
    <p>To ensure a successful delivery and optimal performance of our software services, please ensure that your system meets the specified technical requirements. These requirements will be outlined on our website or in the product documentation. It is your responsibility to verify and meet these requirements before making a purchase.</p>
    <h3>Delivery Confirmation</h3>
    <p>Once you have received your access instructions and successfully accessed our software services, it is considered as confirmation of delivery. Please retain a copy of the access instructions for future reference and support purposes.</p>
    <h3>Contact Us</h3>
    <p>If you have any questions or concerns regarding our delivery policy, please contact us at support@<?=$ihost?>. Our support team is available to provide further clarification and address any inquiries you may have.</p></div></div></section></main>


